_three_fifth  avia-full-contain flex_column_div   avia-builder-el-4  el_after_av_one_fifth  el_before_av_one_fifth  \" style='background: #ffffff; border-width:1px; border-color:#ffffff; border-style:solid; box-shadow: 0 0 2px 0 #9e9e9e; padding:12px; background-color:#ffffff; border-radius:2px; '><section class=\"av_textblock_section \"  itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class='avia_textblock  '   itemprop=\"text\" ><h3>Hiking<\/h3>\n<p><span class=\"drop_cap\">S<\/span>ituated between Malibu and Calabasas, Malibu Valley homeowners can hike, mountain bike or horseback ride from their homes to the famous rock pools in Malibu Creek State Park, have lunch at the M*A*S*H film site and rock climb the Planet of the Apes Wall. Hundreds of movies have been filmed at the park and there are hundreds of miles of trails to explore. Endless adventures await you. After your day outdoors, it is just a short 10-minute drive to Malibu for dinner at Caf\u00e9 Habana or Nobu, or any of the other world-famous dining establishments the area has to offer.<\/p>\n<h3>Wine Tasting<\/h3>\n<p><span class=\"drop_cap\">J<\/span>ust down Mulholland from Malibu Valley are the region\u2019s award-winning vineyards, including Cielo Farms, Malibu Family Wines and Rosenthal Estate. Enjoy wine tasting accompanied by live music and tours of the vineyards. The breath-taking views are indistinguishable from the vine-covered valleys and hillsides of France and Italy.<\/p>\n<h3>Golf <span class=\"special_amp\">&#038;<\/span> Tennis<\/h3>\n<p><span class=\"drop_cap\">W<\/span>ithin 15 miles from Malibu Valley you can spend an afternoon golfing at the Sherwood Country Club, North Ranch Country Club, El Caballero Country Club or the Calabasas Country Club. If tennis is your game, enjoy the beach air of the Malibu Racquet Club, grass and clay courts of the Sherwood Country Club, or the neighborhood feel of North Ranch Country Club, El Cabellero Country Club and the Calabasas Tennis and Swim Club.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/section><\/div><div class=\"flex_column av_one_fifth  av-hide-on-mobile  flex_column_div   avia-builder-el-6  el_after_av_three_fifth  avia-builder-el-last  right-third \" style='background: #ffffff; border-width:1px; border-color:#ffffff; border-style:solid; padding:12px; background-color:#ffffff; border-radius:2px; '><\/div>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":46,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/malibuvalley.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/497"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/malibuvalley.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/malibuvalley.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/malibuvalley.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/malibuvalley.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=497"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/malibuvalley.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/497\/revisions"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/malibuvalley.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/46"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/malibuvalley.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=497"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}